Files:
	client.cpp - main source that creates a socket and retreives HTML file.
	client.h   - a list of useful libraries that were used in client.cpp plus a couple of usefull MACROS (taken from common unp.h library)
	Makefile   - make directives to compile the code, test it, and check it for memory leaks. Also contains a few error management tests.
	myweb      - executable binary that downloads an HTML file. Usage: ./myweb <web url> <IP address>:<port#>/<page i.e.index.html> <opt: -h>